Seasonality Analysis
================================

Row {.tabset }
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

### Inflation
```{r}
forecast_df %>%
  plot_seasonal_diagnostics(.date_var = Date, 
                            .value = CPI, 
                            .geom_outlier_color = "darkred",
                            .feature_set = c("month.lbl", "year"))
```

### Balance of Payments
```{r}
df %>%
  plot_seasonal_diagnostics(.date_var = Date, 
